Package dukechatbot.utility

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Deadline
    The Deadline class implements a subclass of Task that encapsulates the type of tasks that has a specific deadline.
    Event
    The Event class implements a subclass of Task that encapsulates the type of tasks that has a duration associated with it.
    EventTest
    The EventTest class is a test class to test the correctness of the Event class.
    Parser
    The Parser class implements the class that will parse input commands passed to the Duke program.
    Storage
    The Storage class encapsulates the operations on the file to be read and written.
    Task
    The Task class implements the parent class of the tasks to be kept in the task list when the program is called.
    TaskList
    The TaskList implements the operations and attributes needed to handle manipulation of the task list.
    Todo
    The Todo class implements the type of tasks that are to be done but do not have an associated deadline or time component to them.
    TodoTest
    The TodoTest class implements test cases to determine the correctness of the Todo class.
    Ui
    The Ui class encapsulates operations that interact with the client during the running of the program.
